item.title: IP question
item.dc:creator: @Helbound Helbound
item.description:
@Helbound wrote:

[quote=“Rockin, post:16, topic:155078”]It is on[/quote] Try Dynamic DNS. I use them, and they always work.

Website-
http://www.dyndns.com

Create An Account-
https://www.dyndns.com/account/create.html

Login-
https://www.dyndns.com/account/login.html

(WHEN LOGGED IN!) Add A Host (a.k.a- redirection IP [same as no-ip])-
https://www.dyndns.com/account/services/hosts/add.html

(WHEN LOGGED IN!) View your list of hosts-
https://www.dyndns.com/account/services/hosts/

If you need any more help, pm me.
